category: Base
requires: dash  
sdesc: "Incremental autorebase script"
ldesc: "Incremental autorebase script

This package installs a permanent postinstall script to keep the
Cygwin installation properly rebased and additionally provides an
easier interface for triggering a manual full rebase.  The rebaselst
script uses the rebase database and a cache directory in
/var/cache/rebase to record state.

"

